# Privacy Policy

Last Updated: 04/09/2024

## Introduction

This document outlines the privacy practices for the XPeace Bot. This bot is intended for personal use and respects your privacy.

## Data Collection and Use

The bot collects data necessary for its operation, such as:

- Tweets for posting or responding to on Twitter
- Any direct messages sent to the bot

This data is used solely for the purpose of providing the bot's functionalities and is not shared with any third parties.

## Data Retention

Data is retained only as long as necessary for the operation of the bot and is then deleted.

## Changes

We reserve the right to modify or replace this Privacy Policy at any time. It is your responsibility to check this document periodically for changes.

By using this bot, you consent to the data practices described in this policy.
